<view class="page recipes-page">
  <view class="coming-card">
    <image class="coming-spark spark-a" src="/images/decor/sparkle.png" mode="aspectFit" />
    <image class="coming-spark spark-b" src="/images/decor/sparkle.png" mode="aspectFit" />
    <image class="coming-leaf" src="/images/decor/leaf.png" mode="aspectFit" />
    <image class="coming-mascot" src="/images/mascot/fridge-chef.png" mode="aspectFit" />
    <text class="coming-badge">敬请期待</text>
    <text class="coming-title">智能菜谱生成</text>
    <text class="coming-desc">后续会根据冰箱里的库存和临期食材，自动推荐能消耗它们的菜谱，敬请期待～</text>

    <view class="coming-list">
      <view class="coming-item">
        <text class="coming-ic">🥗</text>
        <text>临期食材去化菜谱推荐</text>
      </view>
      <view class="coming-item">
        <text class="coming-ic">🍳</text>
        <text>按现有库存匹配「现在能做什么」</text>
      </view>
      <view class="coming-item">
        <text class="coming-ic">⭐</text>
        <text>收藏喜欢的菜谱</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="settings-card">
    <text class="settings-title">隐私与数据</text>
    <text class="settings-text">冰箱小雷达只保存你录入的食品信息，数据按当前微信账号隔离存储在微信云开发，仅你自己可见，不会收集与库存管理无关的个人信息。</text>
    <view class="settings-link" bindtap="handleOpenPrivacy">查看隐私保护指引 ›</view>
  </view>

  <view class="clear-btn" bindtap="handleClearAll">清空全部食品数据</view>
</view>
